events.name: Clemson Tigers at Boston College Eagles

headlines.description: Deshaun Watson threw four touchdown passes and helped clear the way for Wayne Gallman's 59-yard scoring run with a block and No. 3 Clemson beat Boston College 56-10 on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Watson and No. 3 Clemson take of care business at BC, 56-10

video.headline: Watson's four touchdowns carries Clemson over BC

events.name: Boise State Broncos at New Mexico Lobos

headlines.description: Brett Rypien threw five touchdown passes -- three to Cedrick Wilson -- and No. 19 Boise State overwhelmed New Mexico 49-21 on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Rypien throws 5 TD passes, No. 19 Boise State rolls

events.name: UMass Minutemen at Old Dominion Monarchs

headlines.description: Jeremy Cox ran for a career-high 162 yards and two touchdowns, leading Old Dominion to a 36-16 victory over Massachusetts on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Cox runs for 162, 2 TDs, leads Old Dominion past UMass 36-16

events.name: SMU Mustangs at Tulsa Golden Hurricane

headlines.description: Quarterback Dane Evans went 14 yards untouched for the winning touchdown in overtime, lifting Tulsa to a 43-40 victory over SMU on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Evans TD run in OT gives Tulsa 43-40 win over SMU

video.headline: Tulsa's Evans scores game-winning TD in overtime

events.name: Tulane Green Wave at UCF Knights

notes.headline: GAME WILL BE MADE UP ON NOV. 5
